DROP EXTERNAL TABLE F_Transactions;

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE F_Transactions (
	[SubDepotCode] nvarchar(4000),
	[Depot_Code] nvarchar(4000),
	[Customer_Code_KEY] nvarchar(4000),
	[Customer_Reference] nvarchar(4000),
	[Posting_Date] date,
	[Posting_DateTime] datetime2(7),
	[DocEntry] int,
	[Document_Category] nvarchar(4000),
	[Document_Number] nvarchar(4000),
	[Document_Type] nvarchar(4000),
	[Goods_Receipt_Number_KEY] nvarchar(4000),
	[Item_Code_KEY] nvarchar(4000),
	[Line_Total] numeric(38,6),
	[Supplier_Code_KEY] nvarchar(4000),
	[Supplier_Reference] nvarchar(4000),
	[System_Account_Code_KEY] nvarchar(4000),
	[Transaction_Detail] nvarchar(4000),
	[TransId] int,
	[Type] nvarchar(4000),
	[IR_Number] int,
	[SubIntRecovery_Daily_Budget_Total] float,
	[HorseFlag] nvarchar(4000)
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'DataLake/Structured/Facts/F_TRANSACTIONS_Transformed.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.F_Transactions
GO
